        <h2>About Core Crew Logistics</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Core Crew Logistics</strong> is a full-service logistics provider based in Bakersfield, CA. Since our founding, we have been dedicated to delivering reliable, efficient, and innovative logistics solutions to businesses across California and beyond. Our mission is to keep supply chains moving with precision and care, ensuring our partners can focus on what they do best.
        </p>
        <h3>Our Story</h3>
        <p>
          Established by industry veterans, Core Crew Logistics began as a small team with a big vision: to raise the bar for logistics and freight services. Through hard work, technology adoption, and a customer-first approach, we have grown to serve a wide range of industries agriculture, manufacturing, retail, and e-commerce building long-term relationships based on trust and performance.
        </p>
        <h3>What Sets Us Apart</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Experienced Team:</strong> Our staff includes skilled dispatchers, professional drivers, warehouse specialists, and logistics analysts who work together to deliver seamless service.</li>
          <li><strong>Modern Technology:</strong> We leverage advanced route planning, real-time tracking, and intelligent inventory management to optimize every shipment and delivery.</li>
          <li><strong>Safety & Compliance:</strong> Safety is our top priority. We maintain rigorous standards for vehicle maintenance, driver training, and regulatory compliance.</li>
          <li><strong>Customer-Focused:</strong> We believe in open communication, proactive updates, and rapid response to client needs day or night.</li>
        </ul>
