        <p>
          Core Crew Logistics offers a comprehensive range of services, including:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Freight dispatch and coordination</li>
          <li>Warehousing and inventory management</li>
          <li>Last-mile delivery</li>
          <li>Supply chain consulting</li>
          <li>Custom logistics solutions</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Our People</h3>
